metadata.value: Decoration: Important miniatures, historiated and other borders, initials. Illuminated by Zenobi da Firenze, with the assistance of a painter of the Jacquemart d'Hesdin atelier, fols. 51v and 63, of the Master of Étienne Loypeau, fol. 171v, and of a third hand working in the borders. (P&A i. 637, pl. XLIX).
